Episode XXVIII

THE UNDERCITY RUMBLE


The castle monster was defeated, but Drakkenheim was still dangerous! With a magical item in possession of the DUCHESS, the Queen of Thieves believed she could control the city’s magical defenses.

Talking crab-like creatures lived in the sewers of Drakkenheim. They led the party past a room where a mysterious COLLECTOR dumped new corpses for the inhabitants to eat.

The Duchess’ three blue-haired priestesses described a ritual to speak with the Duchess, and Thurm performed it. They summoned a hydra called the GUARDIAN to ferry the party to the Duchess’ lagoon. Telepathically the Duchess commanded the party to explore the ruined guild-hall and retrieve the Rat Prince’s relic. However the head priestess asked the party to abandon the quest. Weapons were drawn, and combat was about to ensue.
